ProHorizons Website Development Plan
ğŸ› ï¸ Framework Selection for Multi-layered Website
For a multi-layered website with complex navigation and content structure, Next.js would be the optimal choice:

Benefits for your project:
Built-in routing system perfect for complex page hierarchies
Server components reduce client-side JavaScript
Excellent SEO capabilities for better discoverability
API routes for handling data fetching
Built on React, so compatible with your existing knowledge
Great developer experience and extensive documentation
